        public Float estimate​(float progress,

        This function returns the result of linearly interpolating the start and end values, with progress representing the proportion between the start and end values.
        Specified by:

        Parameters:

        startKeyValue - The start value; should be of type float or float
        endKeyValue - The end value; should be of type float or float
